QuestData.Title: Iron Assembly: Admiral Gar'an
QuestData.Description: "If ye want to topple a wall, start with the foundation." It's an old Dwarf saying. If we take out the Iron Horde's leadership, the whole thing tumbles.$b$bGar'an is the Admiral o' the Iron Horde fleet and first of the so-called "Iron Maidens." She, along with her lieutenants, Marak, and Sorka, have dominated the seas of Draenor.$b$bNo more, $n. Travel to Blackrock Foundry and defeat Admiral Gar'an.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Admiral Gar'an in Blackrock Foundry.
